Goal: To redo the NHS organizational platform on SciWeb

Requirements:
    - NHS applicants can apply to NHS
    - NHS admin can review, accept, and reject applicants
    - Teachers can add tutoring opportunities
    - NHS admin can add tutoring opportunities
    - NHS members can sign up for tutoring opportunities
    - All users can request in person or online tutoring

Pages:
    - NHS landing page(Connect >> NHS)
    - Teacher SGI tutoring page

Steps:
    -Account type setting and verification:
        - When someone goes to the Teacher SGI tutoring page whos account type is not a teacher, they will be asked to enter their @schools.nyc.gov email, it will send a verification code to their email, and they will be asked to enter the code to verify their account.

